last_episode_to_air.name: Selling It Like It Is
last_episode_to_air.overview: The finishing touches are being put to Adm's renovated childhood home as 'The Adam Carolla Project' enters its last week. The house is readied for potential buyers, Adam bid farewll to his Loveline radio gig, and his "band of unemployable idiots" gathers for one last flap meat barbecue.

name: The Adam Carolla Project
overview: The Adam Carolla Project is an American reality series featuring the comedian Adam Carolla. The series aired on TLC from October to December 2005.
